				<td colspan="2" height="100%" valign="top"><span class="postbody">If anyone has seen <a href="http://www.kingdomofloathing.com" target="_blank">http://www.kingdomofloathing.com</a> you may know of a time in its past when some exploits were found that generated huge amounts of currency ('meat' in this game) and caused many economy problems. (check it out anyway cause it's hilarious stuff)
<br />

<br />
The solution to this was a series of voluntary things to spend obscene amounts of money on until the economy came back down to a normal level. This deflation worked pretty well, had some rewards for players who participated, and ended up making things much more managable for the normal players.</span><br /><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
